---
title: Campaign lifecycle — one run as a state machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Uploaded: image + description + tone
    Uploaded --> Analyzed: vision + color read the product
    Analyzed --> Segmented: audience builds the persona
    Segmented --> Drafted: copywriter writes two variants
    Drafted --> Checked: guardrails scans the claims
    Checked --> Scored: cta_optimizer rates each call to action
    Scored --> Reported: stored in _run_store, logged to run_log.jsonl
    Reported --> Refining: user moves a slider or sends a request
    Refining --> Checked: re-run the chosen agents (order enforced)
    Reported --> [*]: export campaign JSON

    note right of Checked
        guardrails always
        follows copywriter
    end note
    note right of Reported
        any step that errors still
        reaches a recorded result
    end note
